title: ROH: Supercard of Honor 2024
overview: The 2024 Supercard of Honor was the 16th Supercard of Honor professional wrestling event produced by American promotion Ring of Honor (ROH). It took place on April 5, 2024, at the Liacouras Center in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania and aired exclusively on Honor Club. The event also featured wrestlers from sister promotion All Elite Wrestling (AEW) and AEW's partner promotion World Wonder Ring Stardom (STâ˜…RDOM).
